item.dc:creator: @thebigr5 thebigr5
item.description:
@thebigr5 wrote:

All you have to do to make a .webs.com webclient is make a new page called play- or anything else…
then put the html code in. There is a little box that says html and you have to click that and paste your html code into their. Last just upload the jar and sign via file manager. They dont have to be in the play section or anywhere else, just the main / directory.
